I will follow your lead on this one. <br><br>
Grow Up, Spatz. Notice the absence of &quot;doc&quot;. It is absent because you have caused me to lose respect for you. Believe it or not, it causes me pain to say that. My words on this site for the last year have indicated, in my opinion anyway, a desire for fairness. I have worked hard all of my life to be a man of fairness and patience.<br><br>
Your posts to the Vets on this site, and to Mr Art Varinelli, in particular, indicate the tragic part of the Internet - the part that we like to *deny* when people inquire of us why we bother poring out our guts for all the world to see.<br><br>
I am going to end this message before I say things that are out of character.<br><br>
You owe Art and every other person vet and non vet alike, an apology. Until this is forthcoming, you will receive no further replies from me.<br><br>
One word of advice: let your wife read the type of cruelty you are capable of writing. It is my hope that she will intervene.
